@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title State Machine Diagram: Itinerary Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Create Itinerary
Draft --> Submitted : Submit for Bids
Submitted --> OpenForBids : Published
OpenForBids --> Bidding : Receive Bids
Bidding --> Accepted : Select Driver / Driver Accepts
Accepted --> InProgress : Trip Starts
InProgress --> Completed : Trip Ends
Completed --> Rated : Provide Rating/Feedback
Rated --> Archived
OpenForBids --> Cancelled : Cancel Before Selection
Bidding --> Cancelled : Cancel Before Selection
Accepted --> Disputed : Report Dispute
Disputed --> Resolved : Admin Resolves
Resolved --> Completed
Resolved --> Cancelled
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Archived
Archived --> [*]
@enduml
